{"BAVARDAGE":[{"def":"Much talking; prattle; chatter.","pos":""}],"BAVARIAN":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to Bavaria.","pos":""},{"def":"A native or an inhabitant of Bavaria.","pos":""}],"BAVAROY":[{"def":"A kind of cloak or surtout.","pos":""}],"BAVIN":[{"def":"A fagot of brushwood, or other light combustible matter, for kindling fires; refuse of brushwood.","pos":""},{"def":"Impure limestone.","pos":""}]}